title: Michael Rosenbaum / Spinal Hardware Malfunction
description: Sean talks about surviving "attacks" from the furnace monster. Priyanka tells the spooky story of Wee Willie Winkie. Michael Rosenbaum joins the podcast to share the wild stories of his eight back surgeries and the time his spinal hardware malfunctioned.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
